## Settings

# Set coloring for tab completion
set colored-stats on

# Show all matches in a single column
set completion-prefix-display-length 3

# Perfom file completion in a case insensitive fashion
set completion-ignore-case on

# Show a '/' at the end of directory names
set mark-directories on

# Immediately add a trailing slash when autocompleting symlinks to directories
set mark-symlinked-directories on

# Display matches for ambiguous patterns at first tab press
set show-all-if-ambiguous on

# Denoting a file's type is appended to the filename with a trailing slash
set visible-stats on

# Enable bracketed paste mode
set enable-bracketed-paste on
